Detailed Description

cvmx_vdec::_tc_config_err_flags_reg

This register reports task configuration errors, that occur when a specified parameter value is outside the acceptable range. Different bit mappings are used depending on whether the PHY_MODE for the job is set to LTE, GSM or 3G mode.
